      • PLAY

        static final java.lang.String PLAY
        1. Player chooses with what kind of user he likes to play -Human player to human player PLAY HUMAN [DIM] -Human player to computer player PLAY COMPUTER [DIM] 2. Server: sends wait, when the player has to wait for another player WAIT 3. Server: sends ready when the game can start (this also happens when playing with a computer player) READY 4. Client: responds with READY when they want to start, DECLINE otherwise (in this case the client will get back to the lobby) READY DECLINE 5. Server: requests a move from the user whose turn it is, this message is send to both players REQUESTMOVE 6. Client: Make move with the coordinates MAKEMOVE 7. Server will either send setmove when the move was valid to everyone; invalid move when it was invalid to the user, or not your turn when it was not his turn. SETMOVE ERROR_INVALIDMOVE ERROR_NOTYOURTURN 8. Server: when the game is not over, the server requests a new move. When the game is over its told to both players, and when there is a winner this name is added. GAMEOVER [username of winner] When someone quits the game an error is send and user moves back to the lobby ERROR_USERQUIT The timeout is set on 20 seconds.
        See Also:

      • BROADCAST

        static final java.lang.String BROADCAST
        1.Client sends Broadcast to server BROADCAST 2.Server broadcast chat BROADCAST 3.Client whisper to server to the one who requested it WHISPER 4. Client requests chatuser list CHATUSERS 5.Server sends chat users CHATUSERS [username] 6.Client start game chat via server GAMECHAT 7.Server will support game chat when the user is found,has chat and is in the game, otherwise is the user not found, or he has no chat or he is not in the game GAMECHAT ERROR_USER_NOT_FOUND ERROR_USER_HAS_NO_CHAT ERROR_NOT_IN_GAME

      • CHALLENGE

        static final java.lang.String CHALLENGE
        1.Clients sends challenge to a certain other client via server CHALLENGE 2.Server receives challenge CHALLENGED 3.The client accept or declines the challenge ACCEPT DECLINE 4.If declined the server will cancel the challenge CANCELLED 5.The client asks for status if challenge not canceled STATUS 6. Server sent back the status of the user if the user is found,user is not in an game and the user has option to the challenge function.Otherwise the server will throw an error. STATUS (EG AVAILABLE) USER_NOT_FOUND_FOR_CHALLENGE ERROR_USER_IN_GAME ERROR_USER_HAS_NO_CHALLENGE
